title: How to 5 Pool in StarCraft

steps.headline: Send Overlord to scout start positions.
Wait for 200 minerals to build up, then build Spawning Pool.
Build three (3) sets of Zergling, and enjoy!

text: Build one (1) Drone.  Send Drones to mine minerals.  Send Overlord to scout start positions.  Wait for 200 minerals to build up, then build Spawning Pool.  Build one (1) more drones.  Build three (3) sets of Zergling, and enjoy!  Note: Build 2nd Overlord AFTER Zergling.
